<detall><id label=""><![CDATA[105389]]></id><title label="Titol"><![CDATA[Swap your clothes]]></title><excerpt label="Resum"><![CDATA[<strong>Environment.</strong> It's time for a new edition of the exchange day ‘Renova la teva Roba’.]]></excerpt><content label="Contingut"><![CDATA[<p>Swapping your clothes is really easy at &#8216;Renova la teva Roba&#8217; (Renew your clothes). Take them to the exchange point and they will give you ‘renoves’ for them, the money you will then be able to use to get the clothes you like.</p>
<p>This is a market that will let you reuse, share and consume in a sustainable way. The aim behind it is to encourage conscious consumption and prevent waste. Visitors will also be able to take part in activities, workshops and talks on responsible consumption, creativity and reusing clothes, and preventing waste.</p>
